{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/header_animation.gif?t=1725375805\" /><br><strong>Faraway Islands</strong> is a top-down 2D story driven survival game, set on procedurally generated islands you can travel between and explore. Game contains classic survival mechanics like crafting based on combining, gathering resources and food, farming, hunting animals, increasing character skills, building shelter and defending from enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ADVENTURE</strong></h2>You <strong>play as a survivor</strong> of passenger ship that sank in wild storm. As you try to find a way home from these islands you encounter new friends, that will help you, and enemies giving you a hard time. (character visuals can be customized)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/desc_anim_cutting.gif?t=1725375805\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CRAFT TOOLS</strong></h2>Creating items is done by <strong>combining</strong> or processing items in your inventory. These combinations are not shown to player from start, so you have to try new combinations. Some are recommended to you by story characters or written in quests.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/desc_anim_crafting.gif?t=1725375805\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CONSTRUCTION</strong></h2>You can built your own <strong>shelter</strong> to ensure your safety from predators and enemies. Game has several basic buildings to choose and construct from and more are unlocked by increasing your skills.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/desc_anim_construction.gif?t=1725375805\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORE ISLANDS</strong></h2>All islands are procedurally generated, that means everything from its shape to number of crabs and mushrooms is randomly chosen and then created by predefined rules. Not all <strong>resources</strong> are the same on every island, so you must explore and find what you need.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/desc_anim_map.gif?t=1725375805\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DANGER</strong></h2>Wild animals are dangerous, and you should be cautious when moving around them. So beware that pack of tigers can kill you quite quickly. There are also human <strong>enemies</strong> that will attack every few days. You can prepare for these situations by crafting weapons and armor.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576060/extras/desc_anim_tigers.gif?t=1725375805\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Traveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/1e42416221f07b2b55f6c100a5e73d7a48484168.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/12229c77631065f5845f2bb3cef2cc8c3da46f74.jpg"},{"name":"Got Ya!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/70dd0167dac95223599b8f81bf8577283c279b06.jpg"},{"name":"Bob the Builder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/7610ab0fbf76d201e97713e4d2c52e02461084bd.jpg"},{"name":"S.O.S","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/a17fbb16c3406c5295beddc1d38d265c0e415146.jpg"},{"name":"Measure Twice Cut Once","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/212ac5fd48f453fc56fe77b2746ce1cae3f24bf1.jpg"},{"name":"Bodybuilder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576060/5887ee39ab5a35919c23944751126420dc1eb30e.jpg"},{"name":"Farmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommu